The grass is lush and green, dotted almost uniformly with dandelions in full yellow bloom, giving the scene a cheerful, spring-time feel. Beyond the field is a border of tall, mostly leafless or just beginning-to-leaf trees and shrubs, suggesting early spring growth. In the far left background a low, pale building peeks above the tree line. The sky overhead is a pale, almost milky blue with no distinct clouds visible, and strong sunlight casts a well-defined shadow under the car. Overall, the composition highlights the contrast between the vibrant red of the sporty roadster and the fresh green-and-yellow of the natural setting.=

